    <h1>Creatine for Men Over 40:<br><span class="accent">What It Does, What It Doesn't,<br>and What Most Guys Get Wrong</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">The science is real. The benefits are legitimate. But creatine can't fix the problem most men over 40 actually have.</p>
    <p class="hero-meta">By Robert · May 2, 2026 · 8 min read</p>
