    <h2>How to Take It (The Simple Version)</h2>

    <p>The research on creatine dosing is clear enough that there's no need to overcomplicate it.</p>

    <div class="dose-box">
      <h3>Creatine Protocol for Men Over 40</h3>
      <div class="dose-row">
        <span class="dose-label">Form</span>
        <span class="dose-value">Creatine monohydrate — nothing else needed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dose-row">
