        <span class="dose-value">3–5g per day</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dose-row">
        <span class="dose-label">Loading phase</span>
        <span class="dose-value">Not necessary — reaches saturation in 3–4 weeks at 5g/day</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dose-row">
